§ Ilangi ataasiighmenneghilkata Kiyaghneghmun , Kiyaghneq ataasiighmenneghitesleqatguu ?
§ Yeghlegillu !
Tamaghhaghmi yuuk iqlengiqestengughngaan , Kiyaghneq ipanguuq .
Akuzitni Igaqegkani Kiyaghneghmeng ayuqelghii igaqngaaq whaten , “ Akuzineghpeni , tamaghhaghmi liisimakelleqaaten elqughutnganiluten .
Yuget nanqigtekangaten , ipapighqelleqaten anaggutnganiluki . ”
§ Anaggunnemta , anaggutellemta yuget liigikestengngwaaghaqiit Kiyaghneq elqughutnganiluku .
Enkaam pilleqestaa Kiyaghneq anaggunniluku aghyuuqanginkut anaggutellemnnun ? ( Akuzinguunga yugestun . )
§ Tawatenneghituq !
Kiyaghneq elqughutnganghilkan , natenmi Kiyaghneghem nanqiglleqaki nunam yugi ?
§ Iwernga yuuk pinayalghii , “ Iqlengiqelleghma yuget usuqistaqiit Kiyaghneghmun qayughllak iqlengiqelleghma aliightaqaa Kiyaghneghem ipangullgha .
Enkaam sanganʼngam Kiyaghneghem nanqigtanga aghyuughyaghqaalunga seghleghqestetun ? ”
§ Yuuk pinayalghiillu , “ Seghletun pilta sangwaa pinilghii apeghiighesqelluku seghletun pillemnneng . ” Ilangi yuget temngimeng piiqut whangkuta apeghtughiiqniluta tawaten .
Nanqigtellengyaghqaagut aghyuughyaghqaaluteng , aghyuulleghqamegestun .
